{"title":"Vue 在组件内部更新 body 样式","created_at":"2021-06-24T01:27:55.297Z","content":"<p>首先, 在模板里创建一个新元素:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-html\">&lt;div v-html=&quot;&#39;&lt;style&gt;&#39;+styleText+&#39;&lt;/style&gt;&#39;&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\n</code></pre>\n<p>然后设置<code>styleText</code>的值:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-js\">styleText: `\nbody {\n  background: #ffe4c4;\n}\n`.trim()\n</code></pre>\n<p>你可以动态修改 styleText 的值, 修改后样式会自动更新. 组件卸载后样式也会被移除.</p>\n","slug":"vue-update-background-style-inside-component","category_id":"1","category":{"name":"前端","id":"1","slug":"frontend","alternate":{"en":"frontend","zh":"frontend"}},"alternate":{"en":"vue-update-background-style-inside-component","zh":"vue-update-background-style-inside-component"}}